<link>https://the-decoder.com/ai-systems-rival-doctors-in-new-nature-studies-but-one-result-suggests-the-tech-wont-age-well/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=36749</guid>
<pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 14:37:06 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】《自然》杂志发表的两项新研究表明，在模拟患者病例中，专业AI系统在诊断疾病和制定治疗决策方面与医生表现相当，有时甚至更优。然而，这两个系统所基于的基础模型已经过时。本文《AI systems rival doctors in new Nature studies, but one result suggests the tech won't age well》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/ai-systems-rival-doctors-in-new-nature-studies-but-one-result-suggests-the-tech-wont-age-well/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
