<title>OpenAI 发布 LifeSciBench：含750项任务的基准测试，用专家编写的评分标准评估AI模型在真实生命科学研究中的表现</title>
<link>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/17/openai-releases-lifescibench-a-750-task-benchmark-grading-ai-models-on-real-life-science-research-with-expert-written-rubric/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.marktechpost.com/?p=80587</guid>
<pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 02:28:22 +0000</pubDate>
<source>marktechpost.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【marktechpost.com】OpenAI 的 LifeSciBench 评估前沿AI能否处理真实的生命科学研究，涵盖750项专家编写的任务、七个工作流程和七个生物学领域。该基准由173位博士科学家构建，包含19,020条评分标准，不仅考核记忆能力，更评估推理和决策能力。表现最佳的模型 GPT-Rosalind 通过率为36.1%，在人工制品、精确输出和操作决策方面仍有较大提升空间。本文 OpenAI Releases LifeSciBench, a 750-Task Benchmark Grading AI Models on Real Life-Science Research With Expert-Written Rubric 最早发布于 MarkTechPost。<br/><br/><a href="https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/17/openai-releases-lifescibench-a-750-task-benchmark-grading-ai-models-on-real-life-science-research-with-expert-written-rubric/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
</item>
